1
00:00:00,470 --> 00:00:02,010
(All characters, locations,
organizations, and incidents...)

2
00:00:02,010 --> 00:00:03,510
(in this drama are fictional.)

3
00:00:03,510 --> 00:00:05,080
(This production followed
all guidelines for young actors.)

4
00:00:07,710 --> 00:00:09,150
You wanted to see me?

5
00:00:10,350 --> 00:00:11,550
Han Hye Ra.

6
00:00:11,820 --> 00:00:14,590
Take her down
from the chairman's seat.

7
00:00:15,550 --> 00:00:16,550
Excuse me?

8
00:00:17,490 --> 00:00:19,520
If you do that,
I'll acknowledge you as my daughter.

9
00:00:20,260 --> 00:00:22,190
And I might even consider you
my heir.

10
00:00:23,430 --> 00:00:25,060
Successor to Kunhyang?

11
00:00:26,660 --> 00:00:27,800
What about Se Hoon?

12
00:00:28,070 --> 00:00:30,370
Se Hoon isn't my son. You know that.

13
00:00:32,040 --> 00:00:33,570
You've known all along, haven't you?

14
00:00:34,240 --> 00:00:35,910
That Se Hoon isn't
your biological son.

15
00:00:37,210 --> 00:00:38,380
Of course.

16
00:00:38,380 --> 00:00:40,250
Yet you raised him as your heir,

17
00:00:41,010 --> 00:00:43,280
all the while
planning to cast him aside at will.

18
00:00:44,350 --> 00:00:46,020
Se Mi is too soft and kind.

19
00:00:46,020 --> 00:00:48,090
I didn't want her
in this world of business.

20
00:00:49,650 --> 00:00:51,320
Even though Se Hoon isn't
my own flesh and blood,

21
00:00:52,020 --> 00:00:54,130
I wanted to raise him as my own son.

22
00:00:54,360 --> 00:00:57,060
But he's not cut out for it.

23
00:00:57,430 --> 00:00:59,360
Or is it that you're the one
who gave up on him?

24
00:00:59,630 --> 00:01:01,970
That's right. I don't want...

25
00:01:02,530 --> 00:01:05,240
to hand Kunhyang over
to anyone but me.

26
00:01:06,070 --> 00:01:07,110
Especially not to Hye Ra.

27
00:01:07,970 --> 00:01:10,810
But you love Mom. So why?

28
00:01:10,810 --> 00:01:12,310
I just wanted Hye Ra...

29
00:01:12,810 --> 00:01:14,980
to be protected under my wing,

30
00:01:15,910 --> 00:01:18,020
like a beautiful flower
in a greenhouse.

31
00:01:18,750 --> 00:01:22,520
But lately,
she's been causing me so much pain.

32
00:01:23,460 --> 00:01:25,690
It really gets on my nerves
that she is still...

33
00:01:25,690 --> 00:01:26,790
the chairman of Kunhyang.

34
00:01:26,930 --> 00:01:27,960
So that's where I come in?

35
00:01:29,290 --> 00:01:34,130
Do I seem easier to manipulate
than my mom or Se Hoon?

36
00:01:35,070 --> 00:01:36,870
Even though I was
the disgraceful daughter...

37
00:01:37,640 --> 00:01:39,240
you wanted to kill?

38
00:01:40,840 --> 00:01:41,940
Let the past be the past.

39
00:01:42,270 --> 00:01:44,540
You, my own father,
tried to kill me three times.

40
00:01:45,610 --> 00:01:46,710
How can I possibly trust you?

41
00:01:48,150 --> 00:01:50,550
It's hard enough just trying
to get along with you.

42
00:01:51,780 --> 00:01:53,020
And you want me...

43
00:01:53,850 --> 00:01:55,750
to betray my own mother
to become your successor?

44
00:01:55,950 --> 00:01:58,260
Fine, then say no.
Tell me you can't.

45
00:02:02,090 --> 00:02:04,400
Look at your eyes.

46
00:02:06,130 --> 00:02:08,570
Look at the ambition on your face.

47
00:02:11,100 --> 00:02:15,340
I see myself in you.
Fierce and full of ambition.

48
00:02:17,040 --> 00:02:19,640
If someone hits you once,
you hit back twice.

49
00:02:20,280 --> 00:02:22,450
No, you have the grit
to pay them back tenfold.

50
00:02:23,150 --> 00:02:24,820
You're my daughter, Jung Won.

51
00:02:27,150 --> 00:02:29,750
You belong by my side.

52
00:02:31,290 --> 00:02:32,520
You're a warrior.

53
00:02:34,260 --> 00:02:35,260
Prove it to me.

54
00:02:35,660 --> 00:02:37,060
Taking down my mother...

55
00:02:38,460 --> 00:02:39,730
is how I prove myself?

56
00:02:42,170 --> 00:02:43,300
Exactly.

57
00:02:53,310 --> 00:02:54,750
(Episode 91)

58
00:02:55,550 --> 00:02:57,520
Jin Tae Seok made you
such a ridiculous offer?

59
00:02:57,750 --> 00:02:59,320
(Vice Chairman Joo Ha Neul)

60
00:03:01,950 --> 00:03:03,020
Jung Won,

61
00:03:03,660 --> 00:03:05,660
have you forgotten
how you and your mother made up?

62
00:03:07,560 --> 00:03:11,060
She even drank poison for you.
And you'd actually consider it?

63
00:03:11,260 --> 00:03:13,530
If I were to decide to do that,

64
00:03:14,600 --> 00:03:15,600
would you...

65
00:03:17,240 --> 00:03:19,470
- still be by my side?
- You want me to help you...

66
00:03:20,540 --> 00:03:22,640
take down Chairman Han Hye Ra?

67
00:03:25,280 --> 00:03:26,280
Jung Won,

68
00:03:27,610 --> 00:03:30,580
I want to do anything
and everything you ask of me.

69
00:03:30,920 --> 00:03:32,320
I'd believe your lies,

70
00:03:32,680 --> 00:03:35,690
and I'd stand by you
even if the world turned on you.

71
00:03:35,820 --> 00:03:39,820
- But...
- But you won't help stop my mother.

72
00:03:43,490 --> 00:03:44,560
I need to first...

73
00:03:45,930 --> 00:03:48,670
find out what Jin Tae Seok is
really up to.

74
00:03:58,440 --> 00:04:00,450
He wants to oust Han Hye Ra
from her position as chairman?

75
00:04:00,750 --> 00:04:02,450
And he's using Cha Jung Won
to do it?

76
00:04:02,780 --> 00:04:05,480
What do you think Jin Tae Seok
is really after?

77
00:04:06,250 --> 00:04:08,990
I don't think
I can put my finger on it.

78
00:04:10,890 --> 00:04:14,330
Jin Tae Seok practically
worships Han Hye Ra,

79
00:04:14,490 --> 00:04:17,930
so why would he force Cha Jung Won
to turn on her own mother?

80
00:04:18,560 --> 00:04:19,900
What did Cha Jung Won have to say?

81
00:04:20,130 --> 00:04:21,770
I'm not sure...

82
00:04:21,930 --> 00:04:24,370
if she fell for Jin Tae Seok's trap
or if she has other plans.

83
00:04:24,540 --> 00:04:27,570
- She won't tell me.
- So why are you telling me this?

84
00:04:29,340 --> 00:04:31,910
I need you to find out
what Jin Tae Seok is really up to.

85
00:04:33,750 --> 00:04:36,050
You want me to find out
what Jin Tae Seok is up to?

86
00:04:45,290 --> 00:04:48,490
Why would Gong Nan Sook
invite me to dinner?

87
00:04:49,460 --> 00:04:52,930
I was so impressed
during the retrial.

88
00:04:53,160 --> 00:04:56,230
You really proved
how strong and powerful you are.

89
00:04:57,640 --> 00:04:59,840
Did you think
I'd get provoked by you,

90
00:04:59,840 --> 00:05:01,310
lose my temper, and lash out at you?

91
00:05:02,170 --> 00:05:03,640
Of course not.

92
00:05:03,840 --> 00:05:08,350
It just reminded me
how formidable you are, Chairman.

93
00:05:08,350 --> 00:05:09,780
You're the man! A real boss!

94
00:05:10,750 --> 00:05:12,650
Right this way. Everything's ready.

95
00:05:27,870 --> 00:05:31,200
This is the one and only
Jin Tae Seok.

96
00:05:31,200 --> 00:05:32,370
The Honorary Chairman.

97
00:05:32,440 --> 00:05:34,240
Could you read his fortune
for us, Grandma?

98
00:05:35,470 --> 00:05:37,410
The supposedly amazing
fortune teller...

99
00:05:37,780 --> 00:05:38,910
was you, Chef Hong?

100
00:05:42,350 --> 00:05:43,920
This is amusing.

101
00:05:45,380 --> 00:05:49,190
You'll do everything you want
before you go.

102
00:05:49,920 --> 00:05:51,960
That's right. You're good at this.

103
00:05:52,020 --> 00:05:54,960
Really, Grandma? Wait,
is his fortune better than mine?

104
00:05:55,130 --> 00:05:57,930
I feel like there's more to it.
Isn't there, Grandma?

105
00:05:58,800 --> 00:06:02,070
In the arms of the woman
you love most in this world...

106
00:06:02,330 --> 00:06:03,900
is where you will draw
your last breath.

107
00:06:04,870 --> 00:06:07,610
When? In 100 years?
In Hye Ra's arms?

108
00:06:10,070 --> 00:06:12,640
That's right.
That's just what I've always wanted.

109
00:06:22,990 --> 00:06:24,090
Grandma.

110
00:06:24,960 --> 00:06:27,960
Is Jin Tae Seok going to die
of old age?

111
00:06:28,060 --> 00:06:29,090
No, right?

112
00:06:29,390 --> 00:06:30,830
I wouldn't know.

113
00:06:30,900 --> 00:06:32,200
What?
You're back to being Chef Hong?

114
00:06:32,530 --> 00:06:34,330
I'm dying of curiosity!

115
00:06:34,570 --> 00:06:36,070
Grandma says you should be careful.

116
00:06:36,800 --> 00:06:38,000
Careful of what?

117
00:06:38,640 --> 00:06:41,740
- Avoid water? Or stop driving?
- Careful of your mouth!

118
00:06:43,170 --> 00:06:46,780
Come on, Grandma.
You know I can't keep my mouth shut.

119
00:06:47,280 --> 00:06:48,650
Okay, fine. Just one more question.

120
00:06:49,380 --> 00:06:52,880
Is Jin Tae Seok mortal now?
And I'm more powerful, aren't I?

121
00:06:52,950 --> 00:06:55,490
I don't know! My head is killing me.

122
00:06:56,590 --> 00:06:57,590
Oh my.

123
00:06:58,120 --> 00:07:00,830
Why has Grandma been
so fussy lately?

124
00:07:10,330 --> 00:07:13,000
If I were to decide to do that,

125
00:07:13,640 --> 00:07:14,840
would you...

126
00:07:16,240 --> 00:07:17,710
still be by my side?

127
00:07:19,810 --> 00:07:21,950
Jung Won wouldn't act like this
for no reason.

128
00:07:22,880 --> 00:07:25,420
Is she being threatened? Or maybe...

129
00:07:27,120 --> 00:07:28,120
(Cha Jung Won)

130
00:07:28,120 --> 00:07:31,060
Sorry. I'm tired,
so I'm turning in early.

131
00:07:31,360 --> 00:07:32,360
See you tomorrow.

132
00:07:35,030 --> 00:07:36,460
Something is definitely wrong.

133
00:07:38,000 --> 00:07:39,130
What is it?

134
00:07:47,410 --> 00:07:48,440
Come on in.

135
00:07:48,940 --> 00:07:49,970
(Damga Charcoal Grill)

136
00:07:49,970 --> 00:07:51,510
What's this?

137
00:07:52,040 --> 00:07:55,450
I found this on the street
on my way here.

138
00:07:55,850 --> 00:07:58,020
You found this on the street?

139
00:07:58,880 --> 00:07:59,880
Yes.

140
00:08:00,380 --> 00:08:01,750
How strange.

141
00:08:02,150 --> 00:08:04,220
Who'd drop something like this?

142
00:08:04,290 --> 00:08:06,620
They reminded me of you, Mi Hyang.

143
00:08:08,330 --> 00:08:10,190
Do you not like them?

144
00:08:10,960 --> 00:08:11,960
Take them back.

145
00:08:14,570 --> 00:08:16,200
I don't really like flowers.

146
00:08:16,800 --> 00:08:19,100
I can't accept these,
so please take them with you.

147
00:08:22,170 --> 00:08:23,440
It's from my heart.

148
00:08:26,410 --> 00:08:27,780
I know I'm not worthy,

149
00:08:28,280 --> 00:08:30,850
but please let me stay by your side
for the rest of my life,

150
00:08:31,880 --> 00:08:34,120
so I can atone for my sins.

151
00:08:34,820 --> 00:08:35,850
I...

152
00:08:36,490 --> 00:08:38,220
can never forget Ki Beom.

153
00:08:39,090 --> 00:08:41,160
I'll never forget him
as long as I live,

154
00:08:42,560 --> 00:08:44,000
and my dear Jung Won,
who's gone now.

155
00:08:45,960 --> 00:08:48,270
If you're going to keep stirring up
my quiet life,

156
00:08:48,470 --> 00:08:49,800
then don't come back.

157
00:08:49,870 --> 00:08:51,400
Quit the part-time job
and everything.

158
00:08:53,170 --> 00:08:54,240
I apologize for overstepping.

159
00:08:58,240 --> 00:09:02,210
Oh, dear. Why does he look
so dejected walking away?

160
00:09:08,150 --> 00:09:10,150
You invited Jin Tae Seok
to see Chef Hong?

161
00:09:11,520 --> 00:09:15,890
No matter how gifted he is,
can he really predict his future?

162
00:09:15,960 --> 00:09:20,000
I just feel really strange
about all this.

163
00:09:20,700 --> 00:09:25,070
Grandma definitely said
Jin Tae Seok would die in your arms.

164
00:09:26,240 --> 00:09:28,170
Everyone dies eventually.

165
00:09:28,170 --> 00:09:30,270
But Jin Tae Seok is going to die
in my arms?

166
00:09:31,610 --> 00:09:32,940
I guess that means I'll kill him?

167
00:09:34,280 --> 00:09:37,320
My gosh. That just gave me chills.

168
00:09:37,380 --> 00:09:39,850
That's exactly what
I was just thinking.

169
00:09:39,980 --> 00:09:43,250
I can't believe Gong Nan Sook
is calling me because she's worried.

170
00:09:43,350 --> 00:09:45,860
My son, Ha Neul,
is so worried about Cha Jung Won...

171
00:09:45,920 --> 00:09:47,630
that he's walking around
with dark circles under his eyes.

172
00:09:47,630 --> 00:09:48,930
So how could I just do nothing?

173
00:09:49,060 --> 00:09:50,360
What does this
have to do with Vice Chairman Joo?

174
00:09:51,730 --> 00:09:54,730
Is Jung Won going to eat me alive
or something?

175
00:09:54,830 --> 00:09:56,000
My goodness.

176
00:09:56,000 --> 00:09:58,140
You're not on Grandmother's level,

177
00:09:58,300 --> 00:10:00,440
but you definitely have
a sixth sense.

178
00:10:00,710 --> 00:10:02,610
That's right. I heard...

179
00:10:02,610 --> 00:10:05,310
Jin Tae Seok told Cha Jung Won
to take you down.

180
00:10:05,380 --> 00:10:08,350
Pitting a daughter
against her own mother?

181
00:10:10,110 --> 00:10:11,520
That's classic Jin Tae Seok.

182
00:10:11,580 --> 00:10:13,250
So what are you going to do?

183
00:10:13,280 --> 00:10:15,750
And what is Cha Jung Won thinking?

184
00:10:17,120 --> 00:10:19,690
If Jung Won can go through with it,

185
00:10:19,990 --> 00:10:21,330
I'll gladly...

186
00:10:22,130 --> 00:10:24,660
- let it happen.
- Have you lost your mind?

187
00:10:24,760 --> 00:10:27,670
If I'm not crazier than
that maniac Jin Tae Seok,

188
00:10:29,470 --> 00:10:31,070
I'll never be able to beat him.

189
00:10:32,700 --> 00:10:36,540
You're even crazier than I am.
Forget it.

190
00:10:36,540 --> 00:10:38,280
Hey, one more thing.

191
00:10:38,410 --> 00:10:42,280
I'll have Young Chae divorce
Jin Se Hoon. So...

192
00:10:42,350 --> 00:10:44,750
Young Chae genuinely loves Se Hoon.

193
00:10:44,750 --> 00:10:46,520
You can't stop true love.

194
00:10:47,120 --> 00:10:49,220
This is exhausting. I'm hanging up.

195
00:10:50,960 --> 00:10:51,960
Hey...

196
00:10:53,360 --> 00:10:55,590
Darn it. That woman hung up first
on me again.

197
00:10:56,630 --> 00:10:57,630
Love?

198
00:10:58,060 --> 00:10:59,360
That silly girl, Young Chae.

199
00:10:59,430 --> 00:11:02,130
She keeps ruining her life for love.

200
00:11:02,130 --> 00:11:03,430
And she's still going after it?

201
00:11:03,700 --> 00:11:05,940
Who did she get that from?

202
00:11:07,710 --> 00:11:08,970
Love? Give me a break.

203
00:11:14,350 --> 00:11:17,450
Se Hoon.
I'll still call you my brother.

204
00:11:18,950 --> 00:11:20,380
Se Mi, you found out too.

205
00:11:20,380 --> 00:11:22,620
I'm part of this family too.

206
00:11:27,960 --> 00:11:31,100
I heard Dad already knew,
but he hid it from all of us.

207
00:11:31,600 --> 00:11:33,700
Seriously,
what is wrong with this family?

208
00:11:35,070 --> 00:11:37,500
Are you sure you didn't know?

209
00:11:38,740 --> 00:11:40,100
I only just found out myself.

210
00:11:40,200 --> 00:11:42,510
We lived together for over 20 years.

211
00:11:42,510 --> 00:11:43,870
How could he hide that from us?

212
00:11:45,740 --> 00:11:47,010
Aren't you even angry?

213
00:11:48,080 --> 00:11:50,510
- I am.
- Then why do you seem so calm?

214
00:11:50,580 --> 00:11:51,880
Should I just fall apart?

215
00:11:52,720 --> 00:11:54,020
If I do,

216
00:11:54,490 --> 00:11:56,650
my whole life will fall into chaos.

217
00:11:57,490 --> 00:12:00,930
The parents and family I trusted
would all just fall to pieces.

218
00:12:02,060 --> 00:12:03,490
I can't ever let that happen.

219
00:12:04,130 --> 00:12:07,200
You're a lot like Dad.

220
00:12:08,430 --> 00:12:10,900
I can never tell
what either of you are thinking.

221
00:12:12,900 --> 00:12:15,570
Se Mi. You're my little sister.

222
00:12:16,410 --> 00:12:17,910
Nothing will ever change that.

223
00:12:18,140 --> 00:12:19,880
Mom and Dad are still our parents.

224
00:12:20,080 --> 00:12:22,780
Family isn't only about blood.

225
00:12:22,950 --> 00:12:24,480
That's all I've ever known.

226
00:12:26,180 --> 00:12:28,190
They have no grounds
to just cast me aside.

227
00:12:29,020 --> 00:12:30,250
Who's trying to cast you aside?

228
00:12:30,250 --> 00:12:31,920
Both my father and Chairman Han...

229
00:12:32,820 --> 00:12:35,560
have no intention of letting me
be the successor to Kunhyang.

230
00:12:36,760 --> 00:12:38,360
Right now,
the only one on my side...

231
00:12:39,000 --> 00:12:40,160
is you, Se Mi.

232
00:12:40,360 --> 00:12:42,830
I was worried you were hurt,

233
00:12:43,030 --> 00:12:44,800
but you only care about
being the chairman?

234
00:12:44,870 --> 00:12:46,740
That's your first concern?

235
00:12:46,740 --> 00:12:48,170
It's the same thing.

236
00:12:49,370 --> 00:12:50,980
No one in this family...

237
00:12:51,310 --> 00:12:53,580
sees me as the heir
to Kunhyang anymore.

238
00:12:53,640 --> 00:12:55,850
Who cares about being
the chairman of Kunhyang Group?

239
00:12:56,480 --> 00:12:58,580
I don't care who gets it.

240
00:12:59,050 --> 00:13:01,320
- Jung Won or Ha Neul...
- No!

241
00:13:02,590 --> 00:13:04,050
No one but me...

242
00:13:04,790 --> 00:13:07,830
can be
the Chairman of Kunhyang Group. Ever!

243
00:13:09,160 --> 00:13:10,460
And if they try,

244
00:13:12,160 --> 00:13:13,700
I won't let them get away with it.

245
00:13:28,250 --> 00:13:29,610
Young Chae, what's your game?

246
00:13:31,650 --> 00:13:33,450
Even though I'm not
Jin Tae Seok's biological son,

247
00:13:34,080 --> 00:13:36,550
are you still fine with me
just being Jin Se Hoon?

248
00:13:37,020 --> 00:13:38,020
Or...

249
00:13:39,960 --> 00:13:41,860
does it have to be Jin Se Hoon,
the Kunhyang heir...

250
00:13:42,330 --> 00:13:46,060
and the future chairman
of Kunhyang Group?

251
00:13:47,400 --> 00:13:48,670
I'll be honest with you.

252
00:13:50,830 --> 00:13:53,900
I don't care whether you share
Jin Tae Seok's blood or not.

253
00:13:54,240 --> 00:13:55,240
The only thing I want...

254
00:13:56,370 --> 00:13:58,510
is for you to become
the chairman of Kunhyang Group.

255
00:14:00,680 --> 00:14:03,580
I want you to place Kunhyang Group
right in the palm of my hand.

256
00:14:03,650 --> 00:14:06,050
So you don't love me just for me?

257
00:14:08,220 --> 00:14:09,790
I'm not sure about that yet.

258
00:14:11,020 --> 00:14:13,220
I know for sure that I love you,
Jin Se Hoon.

259
00:14:14,490 --> 00:14:18,330
But I'm not sure I'd feel the same
if you had nothing.

260
00:14:21,370 --> 00:14:24,270
I like how honest you are,
Young Chae.

261
00:14:26,200 --> 00:14:27,270
Alright.

262
00:14:27,810 --> 00:14:32,010
I'll do my best
not to disappoint you, Young Chae.

263
00:14:32,780 --> 00:14:35,010
Even if I'm stripped of
my official heir status,

264
00:14:36,150 --> 00:14:39,180
I'll take Kunhyang Group
with my own two hands.

265
00:14:46,020 --> 00:14:49,190
You mean you haven't found out
what Jin Tae Seok is up to?

266
00:14:49,260 --> 00:14:51,760
He's not the type
to just spill his guts.

267
00:14:52,300 --> 00:14:56,000
But he's planning to go after Han Hye Ra,
using Cha Jung Won.

268
00:14:56,600 --> 00:14:58,070
I already know that.

269
00:14:58,970 --> 00:15:01,370
But Han Hye Ra seems like
she's willing to do...

270
00:15:01,440 --> 00:15:03,970
whatever Cha Jung Won wants.

271
00:15:04,140 --> 00:15:06,680
Seriously, I can't figure out
what's going through her head.

272
00:15:06,780 --> 00:15:08,150
You mean Chairman Han?

273
00:15:08,250 --> 00:15:11,020
She said she'd let Jin Tae Seok win.

274
00:15:11,080 --> 00:15:13,220
But does she even have
a countermeasure?

275
00:15:13,320 --> 00:15:16,020
She and Jung Won may have a plan.

276
00:15:16,190 --> 00:15:18,820
Then why did they leave you
completely out of the loop?

277
00:15:19,160 --> 00:15:22,460
I hope they don't secretly plan
to split the rewards themselves.

278
00:15:22,960 --> 00:15:25,760
You know she's not like that.
And neither is Jung Won.

279
00:15:27,130 --> 00:15:28,900
I'll have to look
into this more closely.

280
00:15:31,140 --> 00:15:33,170
(Kunhyang Group)

281
00:16:03,000 --> 00:16:04,070
Jung Won.

282
00:16:04,070 --> 00:16:06,200
I have a meeting right now.

283
00:16:06,570 --> 00:16:08,640
We can talk later,
Vice Chairman Joo Ha Neul.

284
00:16:28,130 --> 00:16:30,690
You should at least tell me
what you're thinking.

285
00:16:30,930 --> 00:16:34,470
Jung Won is meeting with
the executives behind your back.

286
00:16:34,930 --> 00:16:36,070
I know.

287
00:16:37,300 --> 00:16:39,740
Jung Won is going to oust me
from my position as chairman.

288
00:16:40,270 --> 00:16:41,340
Do you also know...

289
00:16:41,340 --> 00:16:42,910
Honorary Chairman Jin Tae Seok
is behind her?

290
00:16:48,780 --> 00:16:52,280
Does this mean you and Jung Won
planned this together?

291
00:16:52,420 --> 00:16:54,520
We're playing the long game.

292
00:16:54,520 --> 00:16:56,050
So you've formed a united front?

293
00:16:56,520 --> 00:16:57,520
Something like that.

294
00:16:57,860 --> 00:16:59,490
Then why was I left out?

295
00:17:00,360 --> 00:17:03,360
Because I have bigger plans in mind
for you.

296
00:17:03,930 --> 00:17:05,460
What do you mean?

297
00:17:05,800 --> 00:17:07,500
When I step down as chairman,

298
00:17:07,500 --> 00:17:09,100
Jin Tae Seok will nominate
Jung Won...

299
00:17:10,130 --> 00:17:12,200
as the next candidate
for the position.

300
00:17:14,610 --> 00:17:17,110
You know Jung Won isn't cut out
to be chairman yet, right?

301
00:17:17,310 --> 00:17:19,140
She'll need a few years
of training as the successor.

302
00:17:19,740 --> 00:17:22,350
- Then Se Hoon will take her place.
- No.

303
00:17:23,580 --> 00:17:24,780
It can't be Se Hoon.

304
00:17:25,520 --> 00:17:26,750
It has to be you.

305
00:17:28,520 --> 00:17:30,150
You want me to be chairman?

306
00:17:30,850 --> 00:17:33,790
Let's just say it's until Jung Won
is ready to take the reins.

307
00:17:35,790 --> 00:17:37,390
Is that even possible?

308
00:17:37,730 --> 00:17:39,800
You have Chairman Gong Nan Sook
on your side.

309
00:17:40,700 --> 00:17:42,530
It'll go exactly as we've planned.

310
00:17:42,770 --> 00:17:44,330
You think Jin Tae Seok
will just sit back and watch?

311
00:17:45,440 --> 00:17:47,670
He might not even bat an eye.

312
00:17:48,540 --> 00:17:51,070
Jin Tae Seok's Achilles' heel
is Se Mi.

313
00:17:51,910 --> 00:17:55,280
It all depends on whether Se Mi
has a change of heart.

314
00:18:02,420 --> 00:18:04,720
Oh my, what's with the flowers?

315
00:18:04,720 --> 00:18:06,490
Goodness, they're beautiful.

316
00:18:07,260 --> 00:18:08,590
Don't they just scream
Gong Nan Sook?

317
00:18:08,590 --> 00:18:09,930
They're not for you, ma'am.

318
00:18:10,030 --> 00:18:11,860
Really? Then whose are they?

319
00:18:12,260 --> 00:18:14,600
Don't tell me Ha Neul? Chef Hong?

320
00:18:14,630 --> 00:18:17,700
Today is Ms. Young Chae's debut
as a fashion show model.

321
00:18:17,770 --> 00:18:20,600
A debut? Please.
It's just them throwing a party...

322
00:18:20,600 --> 00:18:22,870
in their own company's lobby.
Give me a break.

323
00:18:24,740 --> 00:18:26,240
So you're not going?

324
00:18:26,510 --> 00:18:29,810
Young Chae didn't even invite me.
I'm officially pouting.

325
00:18:32,380 --> 00:18:34,320
What's with the long face?
You look like your world just ended.

326
00:18:34,620 --> 00:18:35,950
You want to go, even by yourself?

327
00:18:36,420 --> 00:18:38,420
Are you serious? Can I go?

328
00:18:38,420 --> 00:18:40,460
You're so happy
that I feel spiteful.

329
00:18:40,460 --> 00:18:41,590
Forget it, you can't go.

330
00:18:41,660 --> 00:18:43,260
You're staying right by my side.

331
00:18:45,560 --> 00:18:48,470
Put these in a vase in my room.
They're gorgeous, just my style.

332
00:18:48,800 --> 00:18:49,800
Hurry up!

333
00:18:54,270 --> 00:18:55,340
Just look at him.

334
00:18:55,710 --> 00:18:57,940
I should set him up soon
with someone.

335
00:18:58,210 --> 00:19:01,650
He's barking up the wrong tree
and has been staring for too long.

336
00:19:01,650 --> 00:19:02,980
His neck must be killing him.

337
00:19:03,380 --> 00:19:04,680
The poor guy.

338
00:19:11,020 --> 00:19:15,390
Jung Won must be heartbroken,
but I'm so proud of her work.

339
00:19:16,260 --> 00:19:18,730
She's been passionate about design
since she was a little girl.

340
00:19:20,730 --> 00:19:24,900
She's so talented,
and I couldn't properly support her.

341
00:19:25,100 --> 00:19:26,900
But she made it this far
all on her own.

342
00:19:27,870 --> 00:19:30,070
Jung Won is a strong person.

343
00:19:30,710 --> 00:19:32,540
Much stronger than we think.

344
00:19:34,780 --> 00:19:36,380
What a nice sight, you two.

345
00:19:37,710 --> 00:19:39,250
Like a mother and son.

346
00:19:39,920 --> 00:19:41,150
Did you get rid of Se Hoon...

347
00:19:41,720 --> 00:19:43,020
and adopt a new son?

348
00:19:43,720 --> 00:19:44,890
Now that's a tempting thought.

349
00:19:45,160 --> 00:19:46,860
(Chairman Han Hye Ra)

350
00:19:46,990 --> 00:19:48,130
I'll let you two talk.

351
00:19:48,560 --> 00:19:50,160
I'm going to check on Jung Won.

352
00:20:06,140 --> 00:20:08,850
The confession at Honorary Chairman
Jin Tae Seok's retrial...

353
00:20:09,010 --> 00:20:10,510
was all thanks to you, Se Mi.

354
00:20:12,050 --> 00:20:15,050
It feels good to hear you say that,
Ha Neul,

355
00:20:15,620 --> 00:20:17,090
but when it comes to my dad,

356
00:20:17,650 --> 00:20:20,420
I'm just so confused and struggling.

357
00:20:21,790 --> 00:20:24,390
Se Mi, do you think
you can help Jung Won,

358
00:20:25,300 --> 00:20:26,300
me,

359
00:20:27,260 --> 00:20:29,370
and your mom?

360
00:20:30,530 --> 00:20:31,800
How would I do that?

361
00:20:33,500 --> 00:20:34,500
Jin Tae Seok.

362
00:20:35,910 --> 00:20:37,810
We're going to make your father
step down.

363
00:20:39,340 --> 00:20:40,910
Your help would really mean a lot.

364
00:20:51,520 --> 00:20:54,860
It's D-Day.
Everything's ready, right?

365
00:20:57,260 --> 00:20:58,330
We're all set.

366
00:20:58,460 --> 00:21:00,560
Joo Young Chae,
aren't you going to apologize?

367
00:21:00,630 --> 00:21:01,700
Apologize for what?

368
00:21:01,700 --> 00:21:04,400
You ripped Cha Jung Won's outfit
and even slapped her.

369
00:21:05,600 --> 00:21:08,510
Do you have any proof that I was the one
who slashed the outfit?

370
00:21:08,510 --> 00:21:10,170
I've already replaced the outfit.

371
00:21:10,870 --> 00:21:13,180
I shouldn't have gotten
into a fight either.

372
00:21:13,310 --> 00:21:14,810
I'd be mad too.

373
00:21:15,080 --> 00:21:16,910
You were the one
who started it, Joo Young Chae.

374
00:21:19,320 --> 00:21:21,080
So self-righteous to the very end.

375
00:21:22,250 --> 00:21:25,590
This is an important day.
That's enough, and let's focus.

376
00:21:26,020 --> 00:21:27,590
Designer Cha Jung Won.

377
00:21:27,890 --> 00:21:30,160
There are no issues
with the outfit, right?

378
00:21:30,760 --> 00:21:32,460
Don't worry, Director Jin.

379
00:21:40,100 --> 00:21:44,510
(Kunhyang Group)

380
00:21:44,570 --> 00:21:46,810
Someone should be out by now.

381
00:21:46,880 --> 00:21:48,450
- Check what the holdup is.
- Okay.

382
00:21:48,450 --> 00:21:50,610
We'll use a strict two-person,
one-person formation...

383
00:22:00,890 --> 00:22:01,990
How are the preparations
coming along?

384
00:22:02,760 --> 00:22:04,560
Where have you been?

385
00:22:05,060 --> 00:22:07,930
- In that outfit?
- It's flashy, but it's comfortable.

386
00:22:08,400 --> 00:22:10,570
I could wear this all day,
and it wouldn't bother me at all.

387
00:22:10,570 --> 00:22:11,970
I'm sure it wouldn't.

388
00:22:14,070 --> 00:22:15,640
Se Hoon is supposed to come, too.

389
00:22:16,210 --> 00:22:18,910
Ha Neul's parents are coming, too.

390
00:22:22,980 --> 00:22:25,080
This is a workplace.
Address people properly.

391
00:22:26,380 --> 00:22:28,490
Who here doesn't know
I'm Kunhyang's daughter-in-law?

392
00:22:33,120 --> 00:22:34,460
How are the preparations going?

393
00:22:34,590 --> 00:22:35,790
- Director Jin.
- Director Jin.

394
00:22:36,060 --> 00:22:38,800
How is everything? No issues?

395
00:22:39,760 --> 00:22:43,600
We managed just fine without you,
Director, so don't you worry.

396
00:22:45,540 --> 00:22:49,240
How about you just hand over
your director position to me?

397
00:22:49,870 --> 00:22:51,270
Stop talking nonsense.

398
00:22:51,340 --> 00:22:53,880
Hey, why would you say that?

399
00:22:54,010 --> 00:22:56,810
You almost let your feelings ruin
an important task at the company.

400
00:22:58,480 --> 00:23:00,920
- Where would you be without me?
- Joo Young Chae.

401
00:23:00,980 --> 00:23:02,420
We'll talk about this later.

402
00:23:03,220 --> 00:23:04,490
Let's just get through
the event first.

403
00:23:05,060 --> 00:23:06,360
Suit yourself.

404
00:23:19,540 --> 00:23:20,600
Se Hoon.

405
00:23:21,670 --> 00:23:23,210
You look beautiful today.

406
00:23:24,410 --> 00:23:26,440
I didn't think you'd actually come.

407
00:23:26,440 --> 00:23:27,580
Thanks for coming.

408
00:23:27,680 --> 00:23:28,950
I'm so happy.

409
00:23:29,310 --> 00:23:31,080
I'll make sure I put on
a great show for you.

410
00:23:41,760 --> 00:23:42,830
I'm so nervous.

411
00:23:43,590 --> 00:23:46,230
- You've worked so hard on this.
- I may have designed them,

412
00:23:46,230 --> 00:23:49,000
but Young Chae made
almost all the samples.

413
00:23:49,430 --> 00:23:50,970
Young Chae worked
really hard on it too.

414
00:23:51,600 --> 00:23:53,540
What am I going
to do with Young Chae?

415
00:23:53,770 --> 00:23:56,070
She can be proud and impulsive,

416
00:23:56,670 --> 00:23:58,110
but she used to be
such an innocent kid.

417
00:23:58,880 --> 00:24:00,640
Should I call it off, even now?

418
00:24:01,080 --> 00:24:03,780
Exposing what Young Chae did
in front of everyone.

419
00:24:06,180 --> 00:24:08,020
She's past the point
of listening to reason.

420
00:24:08,620 --> 00:24:11,760
Young Chae needs to realize
exactly what she's been doing.

421
00:24:13,560 --> 00:24:15,760
She has to hit rock bottom
before she can start over.

422
00:24:26,500 --> 00:24:29,640
Sorry I missed your call yesterday.

423
00:24:32,780 --> 00:24:33,980
I heard from Chairman Han.

424
00:24:34,810 --> 00:24:36,610
Why would you try to shoulder this
all on your own?

425
00:24:38,620 --> 00:24:40,120
Jung Won,
your problems are my problems.

426
00:24:41,120 --> 00:24:42,190
You don't have to
go through this alone.

427
00:24:43,690 --> 00:24:44,690
I was scared...

428
00:24:46,690 --> 00:24:47,890
that you'd get hurt...

429
00:24:48,760 --> 00:24:50,260
because of me.

430
00:24:51,090 --> 00:24:52,530
What I'm most afraid of...

431
00:24:53,800 --> 00:24:55,400
is never seeing you again, Jung Won.

432
00:24:56,470 --> 00:24:57,470
Nothing else matters.

433
00:25:14,050 --> 00:25:15,050
Hey.

434
00:25:23,760 --> 00:25:24,760
Let's get this started.

435
00:25:25,130 --> 00:25:26,130
Already?

436
00:25:27,100 --> 00:25:28,430
There's still some time left.

437
00:25:28,930 --> 00:25:30,500
Cha Jung Won will be back
from the office soon.

438
00:25:30,500 --> 00:25:31,940
Can't the fashion show go on
without her?

439
00:25:33,340 --> 00:25:34,440
I said to just start.

440
00:25:36,770 --> 00:25:37,970
You always have to have your way.

441
00:25:42,610 --> 00:25:44,450
As long as I'm here,
that's all that matters.

442
00:25:44,980 --> 00:25:46,220
Who cares about Cha Jung Won?

443
00:26:37,770 --> 00:26:38,870
The curtains went up.

444
00:26:40,100 --> 00:26:41,870
You haven't changed your mind,
right?

445
00:26:41,970 --> 00:26:44,870
Joo Young Chae has just removed
any last shred of doubt I had.

446
00:26:54,020 --> 00:26:55,520
- What? What's this?
- What's going on?

447
00:27:44,000 --> 00:27:45,740
What's going on?

448
00:27:46,500 --> 00:27:47,500
What's wrong?

449
00:27:52,840 --> 00:27:54,940
(The misdeeds
of Plagiarist Designer Joo Young Chae...)

450
00:27:54,940 --> 00:27:56,210
(have been exposed.
Read the articles.)

451
00:27:58,080 --> 00:27:59,450
Is this about her?

452
00:28:00,120 --> 00:28:01,320
I think it is.

453
00:28:03,120 --> 00:28:05,660
It's not bad.
A little unoriginal, though.

454
00:28:21,000 --> 00:28:22,070
I'll have to make this mine.

455
00:28:24,240 --> 00:28:25,980
(Read the articles.)

456
00:28:39,260 --> 00:28:40,720
(Kunhyang Designer Faces
Multiple Plagiarism Allegations)

457
00:28:40,790 --> 00:28:42,630
(Kunhyang Designer Hired
after Stealing a Portfolio)

458
00:28:42,690 --> 00:28:44,630
(Kunhyang Designer Penalty Canceled?
Light Penalty Sparks Controversy)

459
00:28:47,530 --> 00:28:49,270
(The misdeeds
of Plagiarist Designer Joo Young Chae...)

460
00:28:49,270 --> 00:28:50,630
(have been exposed.
Read the articles.)

461
00:29:09,320 --> 00:29:12,360
(A Graceful Liar)

462
00:29:34,540 --> 00:29:37,050
This is Cha Jung Won's doing!
It's a trap she set for me!

463
00:29:37,310 --> 00:29:38,820
You're suffering
from Ripley syndrome.

464
00:29:38,820 --> 00:29:40,480
Kunhyang Group is mine.

465
00:29:40,820 --> 00:29:42,290
It belongs to me, Joo Young Chae!

466
00:29:42,850 --> 00:29:44,220
Why are you so out of it?

467
00:29:44,220 --> 00:29:45,490
Young Chae, snap out of it.

468
00:29:45,790 --> 00:29:47,560
This is a total disaster.

469
00:29:47,820 --> 00:29:51,030
As long as Han Hye Ra is chairman,
reforming Kunhyang will be hard.

470
00:29:51,230 --> 00:29:53,700
Then we have no choice
but to replace the chairman.

471
00:29:53,830 --> 00:29:55,800
I'm fine nominating...

472
00:29:55,800 --> 00:29:58,640
Vice Chairman Jin Se Hoon
as the next chairman.

473
00:29:58,770 --> 00:30:00,840
If that happens,
Jin Tae Seok will make a comeback.

474
00:30:01,100 --> 00:30:02,740
I have to stop it,
no matter what it takes.

475
00:30:05,880 --> 00:30:07,840
(Subtitles are provided by KOCOWA.)
